      <item>
        <title>SDL: Bolt on or Built in?</title>
        
          <description>&lt;blockquote&gt;
  &lt;p&gt;Time is of the essence. Every day that a business is anything less then fully secure is a day exposed to hackers. It’s also another day that developers continue building applications without factoring security into their lifecycle.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There’s two strategies when you are developing, either you bolt on security, or you build it in. Lets start with defining those!&lt;/p&gt;

</description>
        
        <pubDate>Sat, 03 Mar 2018 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        <link>
        /sdl-bolt-on-or-buit-in</link>
